author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we look back at more sensationalism where journalists fail to truly understand what they look at. Big repositories have come out with millions and millions of account details and you probably are asking how at risk are you at? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: So 183 Million Accounts Have Been Hacked...
